Halo 4 was the first time the Halo franchise had been handled by someone other than Bungie, with Microsoft’s in-house 343 Studios taking the helm. The results were…mixed:

The Good

+Graphics: Halo 4 is one of the most technically impressive games of this generation. Arguably the best-looking game on the Xbox, everything form the character models to the sprawling trademark Halo vistas
